---
title: Beef Tenderloin & Brown Butter Veggies with Cheesy Mashed Potatoes
description: Beef tenderloin is extra special. True to its name, this cut is luxuriously tender—perfect for impressing your dinner companion (and yourself). Here, it’s seared and then drizzled with an ultra-savory shallot pan sauce. Like any great steak-centric meal, however, the sides might just steal the show. We’re serving up creamy Parmesan mashed potatoes and roasted carrots and parsnips tossed with nutty brown butter. Team Add Butter to Everything!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/60510ddde9cc75207965972b-6e0cb6f7.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/beef-tenderloin-brown-butter-veggies-60510ddde9cc75207965972b-f44305b3.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/beef-tenderloin-and-brown-butter-veggies-60510ddde9cc75207965972b
cuisine: North America
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 860 kcal
  fat: 49 g
  saturated fat: 26 g
  carbohydrates: 65 g
  sugar: 17 g
  protein: 42 g
  fiber: 12 g
  sodium: 840 mg
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
